@startuml
actor CustomerManager
participant System
participant Candidate
participant ScreeningProcess

CustomerManager -> System: Schedule Interview
System -> System: Check if interview phase

alt Interview phase ongoing
    System --> CustomerManager: Interview phase ongoing, proceed to scheduling
    CustomerManager -> System: Select interview date and time
    System -> System: Validate selected date and time
    System -> System: Check candidate status in screening process
    System -> ScreeningProcess: Get candidate status
    ScreeningProcess --> System: Candidate status

    alt Candidate passed screening
        System --> CustomerManager: Candidate passed screening, schedule interview
        System -> System: Record interview details
        System --> CustomerManager: Interview scheduled successfully
    else Candidate not passed screening
        System --> CustomerManager: Candidate not passed screening, cannot schedule interview
    end
else Interview phase not ongoing
    System --> CustomerManager: Interview phase not ongoing, cannot schedule interview
end
@enduml